Parameters tunning in NEMoE

cvNEMoE.Rd

This function calculate evaluation of NEMoE object.

cvNEMoE(NEMoE_obj, verbose = T, ...)

Arguments

NEMoE_obj

a NEMoE of object without cross validated parameters.
verbose

A logical input indicating whether the intermediate steps will be printed.
...

Other parameters that can be passed to cvNEMoE.

Value

A NEMoE object with different lambdas.

See also

createCVList

Examples

data(NEMoE_example)
NEMoE_example = cvNEMoE(NEMoE_example, verbose = F)
